

     
      "Gotcha chief."  Hax turns the van toward the on ramp and hits the highway.  He drives for a good half hour and there's no sign of anything untoward.  Then, in the distance, you all spot a car pulled off to the side of the road.  It's a little red two door, tilted up at a funny angle.  There's a jack under the back wheel, the trunk's open and you can see a man standing at the side of the road near the car.  Zara's eye open wide.  "Tom!"
     
    
